{"tid":1908851,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"路邊工程飛出碎石 射爆九巴車窗","createTime":"2020-03-03T14:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T01:45:47.000Z","uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"66f456b6159e82ba71a134c8cf6e53b329422c68","tid":1908851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/03-03-2020/t_b2c2db13edad426f8ed5037e7aee5aa5_name_1583221176_bd90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net%2F03-03-2020%2Ft_b2c2db13edad426f8ed5037e7aee5aa5_name_1583221176_bd90.jpg&h=dfcc5555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一輛17號線九巴，上午11時半左右，行經何文田常盛街途中，疑路中工程有碎石飛出，擊中上層右邊第一扇窗。玻璃頓時碎裂，幸未打穿沒有乘客受傷。女車長隨即駛前到安全位置停下，報警及通知控制室。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查期間找來在場地盤工人了解，初步不排除使用吊臂車時沒有人睇位。事件中一名巴士乘客受驚，一度要求送院檢查，但隨後又拒絕送院。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b91c0686f49d777bc4dc0a5dceee18fecf86943","tid":1908851,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:32:31.000Z","msg":"九龍市區巴士路線17，由九巴營辦，來往何文田（愛民邨）及<span style=\"color: red;\">觀塘（裕民坊）</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，途經何文田邨、常樂邨、馬頭圍、九龍城、新蒲崗（太子道東）及九龍灣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hongkongbus/images/f/f1/KMB_ST5648_17_20170716.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20170717045406&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhongkongbus%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff1%2FKMB_ST5648_17_20170716.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20170717045406%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=99394714&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a52c26c6bebc95ad1eb1929476fa7ba66b17da7","tid":1908851,"uid":82829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"諗真啲梗係拒絕送院啦屌都唔知會唔會野到"},{"pid":"b7724b5f7d79e207aa51b1ac746dab78bff18c2e","tid":1908851,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:33:05.000Z","msg":"諗住唔執輸去左醫院先<br />\n但之後先醒起武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed1a905fb66e0a7539099d81e2f3baa4b19ca0a","tid":1908851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:33:19.000Z","msg":"2018年06月29日<br />\n早上6時，九巴接獲一名男乘客通知，指他乘坐的一輛17號巴士，懷疑座位上有人放置刺針。而該輛17號巴士，早上5時45分由愛民開往觀塘裕民坊，該名男乘客於啟業邨上車，坐於下層座位。男乘客及後約6時20分於創紀之城準備下車時，發現其褲子右邊後袋連著一枚大頭針，他沒有受傷。發現刺針後，他前往裕民坊總站告知站長，站長隨即報警。"},{"pid":"fcbfbacf45278a8ea6eb5822029a572d371e1bd7","tid":1908851,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"依個位好危險<br />\n我揸開車都要小心"},{"pid":"44eff5af4c380bb36dfe264aeb4ae97392f9fb79","tid":1908851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7724b5f7d79e207aa51b1ac746dab78bff18c2e","tid":1908851,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:33:05.000Z","msg":"諗住唔執輸去左醫院先<br />\n但之後先醒起武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/-FuQdGgCXQq3QLpCisVStiJPMhlbBIGERQfVKiuo_qaQtwK6SrRUJ_QJruueteVxHZUx4bLJmeLmKcaj9l-wig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2F-FuQdGgCXQq3QLpCisVStiJPMhlbBIGERQfVKiuo_qaQtwK6SrRUJ_QJruueteVxHZUx4bLJmeLmKcaj9l-wig&h=ab09233b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"924b65077ad8b5884db70fcad9848e3cc8bfc62e","tid":1908851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"一名66歲新巴車長昨晚在深水涉停燈位期間，被一名突然擅自打開車門登車的中年漢揮拳打傷右眼，送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚11時25分接獲事主報案，指當時駕駛巴士到通州街與東京街西交界，在交通燈前停下，被該名突然登車的男子揮拳打傷右眼，對方之後逃去。據悉，施襲的中年漢擅自從車廂外，按動乘客上車車門開關掣打開車門。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，經初步調查，案件列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第七隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4478b1a51877e9803fca39ad75a87480773b1e59","tid":1908851,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:39:31.000Z","msg":"空投師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efeab51faadca1e83d2ada9cfdde3236bb5d11d","tid":1908851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4478b1a51877e9803fca39ad75a87480773b1e59","tid":1908851,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:39:31.000Z","msg":"空投師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Ballista_%28PSF%29_vector.svg/1024px-Ballista_%28PSF%29_vector.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F3%2F3e%2FBallista_%2528PSF%2529_vector.svg%2F1024px-Ballista_%2528PSF%2529_vector.svg.png&h=2c2230f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d7c89ce66db220429a31fb9132f1fd2d1e900dd","tid":1908851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a52c26c6bebc95ad1eb1929476fa7ba66b17da7","tid":1908851,"uid":82829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"諗真啲梗係拒絕送院啦屌都唔知會唔會野到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339448767aacb02b191359e502c8ab849edcedf0","tid":1908851,"uid":59481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老味呢D城市炸彈黎喎<br />\n如果粒石打中左D乘客真係死得"},{"pid":"ce6e240b1722e8033ce399799eaf2fb93bfc0974","tid":1908851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339448767aacb02b191359e502c8ab849edcedf0","tid":1908851,"uid":59481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老味呢D城市炸彈黎喎<br />\n如果粒石打中左D乘客真係死得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T01:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}